00:06:41,426 --> 00:06:44,428
them down. But ultimately whether you're playing as the

104
00:06:44,468 --> 00:06:47,070
cops or whether you're playing as the racers, it's a game about

105
00:06:47,090 --> 00:06:51,992
speed. And at its heart, it's a pure arcade racer. So throughout

106
00:06:52,032 --> 00:06:54,994
the whole game, it was really pure and simple. The motivation

