00:14:36,764 --> 00:14:37,785
was a very different place.

238
00:14:39,026 --> 00:14:44,948
So we knew from other EA titles, we had telemetry showing us that the majority of players, so

239
00:14:45,108 --> 00:14:49,089
on Skate 2, 54% of players had only one friend or zero friends.

240
00:14:49,909 --> 00:14:55,111
So friends, it was just a very early time in how people were using the social features

241
00:14:55,231 --> 00:14:56,812
of Xbox and PSN.

242
00:14:57,392 --> 00:14:58,732
They were just really getting off the ground.

243
00:15:00,178 --> 00:15:01,939
But at the same time, we had social networks.

