00:23:57,888 --> 00:24:00,589
We had a motto for Autolog, and that was connect, compare,

413
00:24:00,629 --> 00:24:00,989
compete.

414
00:24:02,149 --> 00:24:04,230
So this first section, that's about the front end.

415
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:05,830
It's about connecting me with my friends.

416
00:24:10,235 --> 00:24:13,037
When you booted the game, you got this live connected front end.

417
00:24:13,057 --> 00:24:15,918
So it had a load of content that was delivered by web.

418
00:24:16,959 --> 00:24:19,660
And it set the scene by giving you recent updates of what

419
00:24:19,680 --> 00:24:20,961
you'd been recently up to.

420
00:24:21,781 --> 00:24:23,382
And it also gave you refreshes of what

421
00:24:23,402 --> 00:24:24,282
your friends had been up to.

