00:24:47,336 --> 00:24:47,956
really powerful.

431
00:24:47,976 --> 00:24:50,257
And I think that's really important to remember, because

432
00:24:50,297 --> 00:24:52,298
it's a great way for people to spread their passion with

433
00:24:52,338 --> 00:24:56,461
their friends, but also it's got that in common with tools

434
00:24:56,481 --> 00:24:57,722
that you want to build communities.

435
00:24:59,082 --> 00:25:00,923
And that's what we started to see with our photo mode.

436
00:25:02,404 --> 00:25:02,544
So.

437
00:25:03,786 --> 00:25:07,387
Just to show you, these are some of the photos that came up

438
00:25:07,467 --> 00:25:11,108
through dedicated blogs that started popping up about the

439
00:25:11,168 --> 00:25:16,650
artistry of Sechrest County and about the great sites that

440
00:25:16,670 --> 00:25:17,510
could be seen in the game.

