00:25:18,810 --> 00:25:20,191
And then some people take it further.

442
00:25:20,231 --> 00:25:23,752
So a lot of the slides or a lot of the photos on my slides

443
00:25:24,072 --> 00:25:26,373
are from the website deadendthrills.com.

444
00:25:27,327 --> 00:25:29,368
where you've got this guy, Duncan Harris,

445
00:25:29,408 --> 00:25:31,930
and he runs the website, and he goes around

446
00:25:32,050 --> 00:25:33,351
taking screenshots from games

447
00:25:33,371 --> 00:25:34,752
that have good screenshot capabilities.

448
00:25:34,792 --> 00:25:36,494
He doesn't touch any of them in Photoshop,

449
00:25:37,254 --> 00:25:41,978
and he just makes an art out of taking screenshots.

450
00:25:42,478 --> 00:25:43,939
And so then, by having these tools,

451
00:25:43,999 --> 00:25:45,380
you're allowing your community

452
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:48,463
and those outstanding individuals in your community

453
00:25:49,003 --> 00:25:52,245
to do this stuff and make your game look fantastic,

454
00:25:52,265 --> 00:25:54,647
and then share the best of your game with everyone else.

455
00:25:56,168 --> 00:25:56,909
So that was really cool.

456
00:25:57,887 --> 00:25:59,188
It was nice to see those.

